                    </div>
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="debat-tentang-kenaikan-bbm-berikan-contoh-pendapat-pro-kontra-netral">
                            1. Debat tentang kenaikan bbm berikan contoh pendapat pro kontra netral</h2><br />
                        <p>pro : kenaikan harga bbm sangat efektif guna meningkatkan perekonomian indonesia</p><p>kontra : kenaikan harga bbm malah hanya akan menyusahkan rakyat</p><p>netral : kenaikan harga bbm sebenarnya tdk membawa pengaruh negatif maupun positif bagi masyarakat,tinggal kita saja yg menyiasati-nya</p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="kenaikan-harga-bbm-semakin-menyulitkan-ekonomi-masyarakat-pro-kontra-nya-apa%e2%80%8b">
                            2. kenaikan harga BBM semakin menyulitkan ekonomi masyarakat. pro kontra nya apa??​</h2><br />
                        <p>pro-nya adalah kenaikan BBM dapat menaikkan devisa negara , setelahnya bisa mengurangi penggunaan minyak bumi dan mengurangi pencemaran lingkungan oleh kendaraan karena banyak masyarakat yang beralih ke mobil angkutan umum</p><p>kontra nya adalah banyak masyarakat yang tidak puas akan kenaikan BBM dan akan menyebabkan kerusuhan , karena kenaikan BBM  bisa menaikkan harga pokok lainnya dan kebutuhan masyarakat </p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="contoh-percakapan-tentang-pro-dan-kontra-kenaikan-bbm">
                            3. contoh percakapan tentang pro dan kontra kenaikan BBM </h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, netizens who rejected the increase in subsidized fuel prices expressed sarcasm and protests against Jokowi and his voters, and considered that this policy would bring misery to the people. As of Tuesday afternoon, #SalamGigitJari reached 60,900 conversations, BBM increased by 400,000, and #ShameOnYouJokowi reached 46,200 conversations. President Joko Widodo raised the price of subsidized fuel, namely Premium and Solar by IDR 2,000. Premium prices increased from IDR 6,500 to IDR 8,500 and diesel from IDR 5,500 to IDR 7,500. Before the increase was made, Jokowi said the government had prepared a non-cash assistance package for around 15 million poor people, through the KKS Prosperous Family Card, the KIP Smart Indonesia Card, and the KIS Healthy Indonesia Card. Meanwhile, Minister of Finance Bambang Brodjonegoro told reporters at the Palace that the budget that had been used for fuel subsidies would be diverted to productive spending.</p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p><strong>maaf</strong><strong> </strong><strong>kalo</strong><strong> </strong><strong>salah</strong></p><br />
